
<div class="container-show-text">
    <h4 class="header-text"><medium><%= @chef.first_name %> <%= @chef.last_name %></medium></h4>
    <h6 class="sub-header-text"><%= @chef.restaurant.name %> - <%= @chef.restaurant.location %> </h6>
</div>

<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div
      class="chef-show-img"
      style="background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path(@chef.menus[0].photos[0].key, crop: :fill )%>')">
    </div>
    <div
      class="chef-show-img"
      style="background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path(@chef.menus[0].photos[1].key, crop: :fill )%>')">
    </div>
</div>

<div class="spacing-show">
</div>

<div class="container-show-story">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div>
      <div class="chef-show-img-profile"
          style="background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path(@chef.photos[0].key, crop: :fill )%>')">
      </div>
        <div class=below-chef-img>
          <a href="#">
            <i class="fab fa-fw fa-instagram"></i>
          </a>
            <a href="#">
            <i class="fab fa-pinterest"></i>
          </a>
            <small>1.7k Chef's plate followers</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  <p class="story-text">
    I learnt to cook on the job and moved from restaurant to restaurant in London working my way up.  My stint at the Ritz is what really propelled my skill and I began to experiment with vegan dishes as mains.
  <br>
  <br>
    My love for cooking began when I was 14.  I used to go fishing with my father and I became obssessed.  I used to spend hours prepping the fish before he used to cook  them.  I grew a profound respect for the animal and the way their enviroment influenced their flavour.
  <br>
  <br>
    My favourite ingredients these days consists of wild scottish salmon, hard to find the good quality these days.  I love forraged ingredients and our supplier picks qild samphire and oyster mushrooms from down in Cornwall, the location being a closely guarded secret!
  </p>
    <div>

      <%= link_to "Book table", "", class: "book-table" %>

      <div class="chef-insight">
        <p><strong> Chef's plate insight </strong></p>
        <p> Our pasta chef has a acquired a rare italian flower we are using with our lobster ravioli.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chef-name-signature">
    <%= @chef.first_name %> <%= @chef.last_name %>
  </div>
</div>

